    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly your <strong>Warhawk</strong> ship, pew pew... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >based on the award winning Commodore 64 game, enhanced and brought to the PC and the ZX Spectrum Next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game has been carefully renovated from its original 1986 release by one of the developers of the original game, whilst also retaining its original feel and hectic playability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Featuring</u> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 frantic levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 large bosses and 10 mini bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glorious music throughout </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-stop blasting action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An army of dangerous enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stunning 8-bit graphics </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game also includes wallpapers  along with the entire soundtrack album.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032240/extras/345fba5da2f534263c1cd130e988151c.avif?t=1741377795\" width=512 height=512 /></span></p>",
